{"article_id":"5menwyvNz9Cv4T0C","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"President Trump ,","depth":6},{"id":1,"text":"who was on Air Force One en route to a rally in Kansas","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"while the Senate voted on Judge Kavanaugh ,","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"invited reporters aboard the flight","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"to watch the vote in his office in the front of the plane .","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"After Vice President Mike Pence announced","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"that Judge Kavanaugh had been confirmed ,","depth":6},{"id":7,"text":"the president flashed reporters a thumbs up","depth":6},{"id":8,"text":"as aides applauded .","depth":6},{"id":9,"text":"\" Great decision , \"","depth":6},{"id":10,"text":"Mr. Trump said .","depth":6},{"id":11,"text":"He said","depth":6},{"id":12,"text":"Judge Kavanaugh would \" go down as a totally brilliant Supreme Court justice for many years , \"","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"adding","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"that he had chosen the judge for his \" temperament , his incredible past , his outstanding years on the court . \"","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"Mr. Trump added","depth":6},{"id":16,"text":"that he was \" honored \"","depth":7},{"id":17,"text":"Judge Kavanaugh had been able to \" withstand \" the allegations of sexual assault against him ,","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"which the president called a \" horrible , horrible attack by the Democrats . \"","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"Asked about women angry about the outcome of the vote ,","depth":7},{"id":20,"text":"Mr. Trump said :","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"\" I don ' t think","depth":9},{"id":22,"text":"they are. \"","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"He said","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"women were \" outraged at what happened to \" Judge Kavanaugh","depth":10},{"id":25,"text":"and that they were \" in many ways stronger than the men in his favor . \"","depth":10},{"id":26,"text":"The president said","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"women were \" extremely happy \"","depth":11},{"id":28,"text":"that Judge Kavanaugh had been able to move past the allegations against him","depth":11},{"id":29,"text":"\" because they ' re thinking of their sons ,","depth":11},{"id":30,"text":"they ' re thinking of their husbands and their brothers , their uncles , and others . \"","depth":11},{"id":31,"text":"Mr. Trump said","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"he was \" 100 % \" certain","depth":10},{"id":33,"text":"that the allegations against the new Supreme Court justice were not true ,","depth":10},{"id":34,"text":"saying","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"the FBI had done an \" excellent job \"","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"-- and","depth":11},{"id":37,"text":"that","depth":12},{"id":38,"text":"if they were true ,","depth":13},{"id":39,"text":"\" that would have come out loud and clear \" in the past decades","depth":14},{"id":40,"text":"he has spent as a judge .","depth":14},{"id":41,"text":"President Trump called Judge Kavanaugh","depth":6},{"id":42,"text":"following the Senate vote","depth":6},{"id":43,"text":"to congratulate him ,","depth":5},{"id":44,"text":"the White House said .","depth":4},{"id":45,"text":"Mr. Trump ,","depth":6},{"id":46,"text":"who signed the judge ' s commission aboard Air Force One on his way to the rally ,","depth":6},{"id":47,"text":"also spoke to Vice President Mike Pence , Senate Majority Leader Mitch McConnell and House Speaker Paul Ryan .","depth":5},{"id":48,"text":"Also while aboard the flight , the president in a tweet taunted a crowd of protesters in front of the Supreme Court .","depth":5},{"id":49,"text":"\" The crowd in front of the U.S. Supreme Court is tiny ,","depth":9},{"id":50,"text":"looks like about 200 people","depth":10},{"id":51,"text":"( & most are onlookers ) -","depth":10},{"id":52,"text":"that wouldn ' t even fill the first couple of rows of our Kansas Rally , or any of our Rallies for that matter ! \"","depth":8},{"id":53,"text":"Mr. Trump wrote .","depth":7},{"id":54,"text":"\" The Fake News Media tries to make it look sooo big ,","depth":7},{"id":55,"text":"& it ' s not ! \"","depth":7},{"id":56,"text":"Hundreds of people protested on Saturday ,","depth":3},{"id":57,"text":"with police arresting 150 on the steps of the Capitol and another 13","depth":4},{"id":58,"text":"who chanted during the vote.","depth":4},{"id":59,"text":"In the last two weeks Capitol Police have arrested hundreds of demonstrators , some 300 alone on Thursday","depth":4},{"id":60,"text":"when Senators had the chance","depth":5},{"id":61,"text":"to review the FBI report on the sexual misconduct allegations against Judge Kavanaugh ,","depth":5},{"id":62,"text":"and another 100 on Friday .","depth":3}],"relations":[{"parent":125,"left":118,"right":124,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":118,"left":103,"right":117,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":103,"left":71,"right":102,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":71,"left":67,"right":70,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":67,"left":65,"right":66,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":65,"left":0,"right":64,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":64,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":66,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":70,"left":68,"right":69,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":68,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":69,"left":7,"right":8,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":102,"left":76,"right":101,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":76,"left":72,"right":75,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":72,"left":9,"right":10,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":75,"left":11,"right":74,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":74,"left":12,"right":73,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":73,"left":13,"right":14,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":101,"left":79,"right":100